    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">In</supplied> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Deo Santio <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">G</supplied>enio |(centuriae) <supplied reason="lost">L</supplied>u<supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>i<lb break="no" n="3"/>[li<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> ------
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Rückseite des Steines im Mittelalter sekundär bearbeitet. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. (B): Beckmann: Z. 3: [et G]enio | Luc/[ilii; Schmidt Heidenreich: Z. 1: [In h(onorem)]; Z. 3: [Ge]nio (centuriae) Luci/[li(i)?; Leonhard: Z. 3: Genio (centuriae) Luci/[li?. Autopsie R. Wiegels; Hauptbearbeiterin: B. Esch.</p>
            </div>
